## Segments

- **hello-intro** -- Title card with animated entrance
- **hello-outro** -- Closing card with call to action

## Running

```bash
npx videowright dev videos/{{video_name}}/timeline.ts
```

## Editing

- Edit segments in `segments/hello-intro/index.ts` and `segments/hello-outro/index.ts`
- Add new segments to `segments/<name>/index.ts` and wire them in `timeline.ts`
- The dev server reloads automatically on file changes
